The '''Roman Catholic Diocese of Blumenau''' ({{lang-la|Florumpraten(sis)}}) is a [[diocese]] located in the city of [[Blumenau]] in the [[Ecclesiastical province]] of [[Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Florian<U+00F3>polis|Florian<U+00F3>polis]] in Brazil.

==History==
* April 19, 2000: Established as Diocese of Blumenau from the Metropolitan Archdiocese of Florian<U+00F3>polis, [[Diocese of Joinville]] and [[Diocese of Rio do Sul]]

==Leadership==
* [[Bishop]]s of Blumenau (Roman rite)
** Bishop Ang<U+00E9>lico S<U+00E2>ndalo Bernardino (April 19, 2000 <U+2013> present)

